g-Tooltip An Extension
INTRODUCTION
A plugin module for jQuery for nice looking Tooltips instead of the traditional dull ones
FEATURES
* Easy to setup
* No additional css markup needed
* Tested on Firefox, Chrome and IE 9
* No need to write long javascript routines, just add it between <head></head> tags.
	<script type="text/javascript" src="path to g-Tooltips.js" />
* Simply invoke the plugin in your document onLoad event and it will take care of everything
	$(document).ready(function() {
		$('your element/s here').forgeTooltips();
	});
* Don't like default background color and you want to change the opacity as well as orientation? Not an issue
	$(document).ready(function() {
		var options = { orientation:'top', backgroundColor:'#007543', opacity:0.8  };
		$('your element/s here').forgeTooltips(options);
	});
	* Please be advised left orientation is not working right now but top, bottom and right positioning works fine, that will be covered in the next release
* Multiple elements support in single call.
	$('body button[title],body input[title],body a[title]').forgeTooltips(options);
	Easy as it looks!
